詹姆斯·米勒之死
The death of James Miller,

49
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:59,850
所谓的哈里发国对东首都电信的攻击
the so-called ICO attack at Capital East Telecom network...

50
00:03:59,850 --> 00:04:02,510
等等  你是说哈里发国不是罪魁祸首
Wait, wait, wait. Are you saying ICO wasn't responsible?

51
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:03,750
我是说这不重要
I'm saying it doesn't matter.

52
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,550
网络通讯在总统眼皮底下瘫痪掉了
The Internet went down on the president's watch.

53
00:04:06,550 --> 00:04:08,730
-你不觉得哈里发国  -听着  弗莱德
- Don't you think ICO was-- - Now listen, Fred--

54
00:04:08,730 --> 00:04:10,560
不  哈里发国才是真正的威胁
